  "prompt": "Which tickets were sold by BookMyShow for Global Citizen Festival?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **BookMyShow** offers a variety of ticket options for events like the **Global Citizen Festival**. While the specific ticket types can vary based on the venue, date, and organizers' offerings, here are some common categories you might find:\n\n1. **General Admission (GA):**\n   - **Description:** These tickets provide access to the main event area without assigned seating. It's a great option for attendees who prefer flexibility.\n   - **Features:** Standing or lawn seating areas, access to all general event activities.\n\n2. **VIP Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** VIP tickets offer enhanced experiences compared to general admission.\n   - **Features:** Reserved seating, exclusive access to VIP lounges or areas, complimentary food and beverages, merchandise, meet-and-greet opportunities with artists or special guests.\n\n3. **Premium Seating:**\n   - **Description:** These are high-tier tickets with assigned seats offering better views of the stage.\n   - **Features:** Reserved seating in prime locations, possibly closer proximity to the stage, access to premium amenities.\n\n4. **Group Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Designed for larger groups attending together, often with discounted rates.\n   - **Features:** Bundle pricing, reserved seating for the group, sometimes additional perks like group photos or shout-outs.\n\n5. **Early Bird Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Available at reduced prices for a limited time before the main sale starts.\n   - **Features:** Lower pricing, limited quantity, first-come-first-served basis.\n\n6. **Accessible Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Catering to attendees with disabilities.\n   - **Features:** Reserved seating with accessibility considerations, assistance services, designated entrances and exits.\n\n7. **Sponsorship or Partner Packages:**\n   - **Description:** Special packages for corporate sponsors or partners.\n   - **Features:** Branding opportunities, dedicated spaces, complimentary tickets for guests or employees.\n\n8. **Merchandise Bundles:**\n   - **Description:** Tickets bundled with official event merchandise.\n   - **Features:** T-shirts, posters, commemorative items included with the ticket purchase.\n\n**How to Purchase:**\n\nTo view the current ticket offerings for the **Global Citizen Festival** on BookMyShow:\n\n1. **Visit the BookMyShow Website or App:**\n   - Navigate to [BookMyShow](https://www.bookmyshow.com/) and use the search bar to find the Global Citizen Festival event.\n\n2. **Select the Event:**\n   - Click on the specific event listing to view detailed information.\n\n3. **Choose Your Ticket Type:**\n   - Browse through the available ticket categories, select your preferred option, and proceed to purchase.\n\n4. **Review and Confirm:**\n   - Ensure all details are correct before finalizing your purchase. You may receive electronic tickets or a booking confirmation via email or the app.\n\n**Additional Tips:**\n\n- **Stay Updated:** Event organizers may release different ticket types or special promotions leading up to the event date. Regularly check the BookMyShow listing for updates.\n  \n- **Sign Up for Notifications:** Consider creating an account on BookMyShow and signing up for notifications to receive alerts about ticket sales, discounts, and exclusive offers.\n\n- **Contact Support:** If you have specific questions or require assistance, BookMyShow's customer support can provide personalized help. Visit their [Help Center](https://support.bookmyshow.com/) for more information.\n\n**Note:** Availability and types of tickets can vary based on several factors, including location, venue capacity, and event-specific arrangements. Always refer to the official BookMyShow platform for the most accurate and up-to-date information.",
